#: ../../language/error_codes/E4184.md:1
msgid "E4184"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4184.md:3
msgid ""
"Compiler diagnostic name: "
"`start_rest_binder_is_not_supported_in_longest_match_strategy`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4184.md:5
msgid ""
"A leading rest binder is not supported with the longest-match `lexmatch` "
"strategy."
msgstr "最长匹配策略的 `lexmatch` 不支持开头的剩余绑定器。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4184.md:8
msgid ""
"In `lexmatch ... with longest`, the engine chooses the longest matching "
"case. Allowing a rest binder before the regex would make that choice "
"ambiguous, so the start rest binder is rejected."
msgstr ""
"在 `lexmatch ... with longest` 中，引擎会选择最长的匹配分支。允许在正则前"
"出现剩余绑定器会让这个选择变得含糊，因此开头的剩余绑定器会被拒绝。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4184.md:12
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4184.md:14
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn match_text(text : String) -> Unit {\n"
"  lexmatch text with longest {\n"
"    (_, \"abc\", _) => ()\n"
"    _ => ()\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4184.md:18
msgid ""
"The first `_` attempts to bind or skip input before the `\"abc\"` regex "
"pattern."
msgstr "第一个 `_` 试图在 `\"abc\"` 正则模式之前绑定或跳过输入。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4184.md:20
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "修改建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4184.md:22
msgid ""
"Match the regex at the start of the remaining input, and bind only the "
"suffix when needed."
msgstr "让正则从剩余输入的开头开始匹配，并且只在需要时绑定后缀。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4184.md:25
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn match_text(text : String) -> Unit {\n"
"  lexmatch text with longest {\n"
"    (\"abc\", _) => ()\n"
"    _ => ()\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
